data.description: What a potential investment opportunity in this Pool home with NO deed restrictions, in one of the most desirable areas of town.. Close to the boat ramps and the area beaches, just off Riverview Blvd.  Save money on storage fees and park your RV or boat at home under a large carport with 100 amp sub panel with 120V & 50 amp service.  Do you work from home or in business? The detached garage & workshop with roll up door, and electric with plenty of storage will be perfect for your needs.  Boasting a fenced backyard paradise complete with an inviting private pool surrounded by lush tropical foliage.  A covered sitting area to relax around adjacent to a dedicated spot for an outdoor kitchen is ideal for hosting outdoor activities and creating lasting memories. A Gardeners delight with your own area complete with a potting bench. The little ones can also enjoy the fenced play area. Coming in from a long day on the boat? Rinse off in the outdoor shower before you jump in the pool.  The living room, dining room, kitchen are beautifully interconnected, creating an open and welcoming atmosphere. Natural light floods the space through large windows, offering picturesque views of the surrounding beauty. Enjoy a delightful pool & garden view from the dining room. Convenience is a priority in this home, with a mudroom/laundry room and den/office situated off of the kitchen. Whether you need a dedicated workspace, playroom or another bedroom for the little ones, this versatile space accommodates your needs with ease. The split bedroom 2/2 floor plan provides privacy for everyone.   Updates include newer windows, 200 amp service with surge protection, all new electric outlets, and led can lights with dimmers. Location is key, and this home is perfectly situated near Warner's Bayou boat ramp, Manatee River, Robinson Preserve, shops, restaurants and schools. The stunning beaches of Anna Maria Island are just a short distance away, allowing you to indulge in the coastal lifestyle whenever you desire. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this beautiful property your Florida dream come true!  Seller is motivated make an offer!
